MYR is an educational tool that strikes a balance with the ease of use and challenge. We drew inspiration from Logo Turtle and Processing to provide a beginner friendly experience for teaching and learning with MYR. If you want to learn more about MYR itself, visit our
Within the editor you can create 3D scenes using JavaScript and the MYR API. You can then view your scene in the viewer using a computer, tablet, smartphone, or a VR headset.
MYR is being developed by the
